# the hierarchy under my home directory
# cf. Filesystem Hierarchy Standard

~
    /local
            uploaded to github.com
        /bin
                binaries I wrote
        /share
            /doc
                    contains this file
    /tmp
            working in the root of home is too dangerous
    /work
    /var
            non-uploadable config files: history files, browser configs, etc.
    /bin
            binaries others wrote
    /share
            misc files others wrote: documents, sources, etc.
    /lib
            heavy executable files
